{"word":"ἐνδέξιος","slug":"ἐνδέξιος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n35150\" key=\"e)nde/cios\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐνδέξιος</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">α</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> only neut. pl. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐνδέξια</foreign>, <sense id=\"n35150.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">towards the right hand, from left to right</tr_>, mostly as <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">θεοῖς ἐνδέξια πᾶσιν οἰνοχόει</foreign> he filled for all the gods <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">from left to right</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:597\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.597</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">δεῖξ᾽ ἐνδέξια πᾶσιν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:184\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.184</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">βῆ δ᾽ ἴμεν αἰτήσων ἐνδέξια φῶτα ἕκαστον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:17:365\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.365</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὴν ἐπὶ πυρκαϊῆς ἐ. φασι κέλευθον Ἑρμῆν τοὺς ἀγαθοὺς . . ἄγειν</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIfor